headline: Intuit Begins Fiscal 2025 on a Strong Note: Time to Buy or Hold?
summary: Intuit kicks off FY25 with 10% revenue growth, driven by AI innovation and 20% online ecosystem expansion. Mid-market success and robust Credit Karma gains signal growth potential for 2025.

headline: Intuit TurboTax Launches "Now This Is Taxes" Campaign Showcasing Its Revolutionary New Taxes 'Done-For-You' Experiences at Unbeatable Prices
summary: MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif., December 30, 2024--Intuit Inc.
